✅ FormaFit Website – Registration Form Test Cases
1. Full Name Field Validation
- TC001: Verify that the Full Name field accepts only alphabetic characters and spaces
- TC002: Verify that entering numbers or special characters triggers a validation error
- TC003: Verify minimum and maximum character limits (e.g., 2–50 characters)
- TC004: Verify that leading/trailing spaces are trimmed automatically
- TC005: Verify placeholder text and label visibility on all screen sizes
2. Phone Number Field Validation
- TC006: Verify that only numeric input is accepted
- TC007: Verify that the field enforces a 10-digit format for Indian numbers
- TC008: Verify error message when entering fewer or more than 10 digits
- TC009: Verify that country code is either auto-filled or selectable
- TC010: Verify that copy-paste and autofill do not bypass validation
3. Email Field Validation
- TC011: Verify that valid email formats are accepted (e.g., user@example.com)
- TC012: Verify error message for invalid formats (e.g., missing “@” or domain)
- TC013: Verify duplicate email detection if already registered
- TC014: Verify that email field is case-insensitive
4. Password Field Validation
- TC015: Verify minimum password length (e.g., 8 characters)
- TC016: Verify complexity rules (uppercase, lowercase, number, symbol)
- TC017: Verify visibility toggle (eye icon) works correctly
- TC018: Verify error messages for weak passwords
5. Form Submission & UX
- TC019: Verify that all required fields must be filled before enabling Submit
- TC020: Verify loading indicator and success message after submission
- TC021: Verify redirection to dashboard or confirmation page
- TC022: Verify responsiveness across devices (mobile, tablet, desktop)
- TC023: Verify accessibility (keyboard navigation, screen reader labels)
